    "When the normal and abnormal distributions are completely separated, τ I may exceed τ σ.",
    "Therefore, the lower bound of τ σ is set to τ I.",
    "We assign a weight w i = 0 for hard rejection and w i = t s for soft rejection.",
    "Finally, the model is trained using a weighted loss function.",
    "EvaluationThis section compares existing sample selection methods and robust loss functions with our methods."
